au.gov.ansto.bragg.cicada.export
Interface Formater

All Superinterfaces:
au.gov.ansto.bragg.base.common.All, Common, au.gov.ansto.bragg.base.common.Publisher, java.io.Serializable
public interface Formater
extends Common

An interface for Formater_ class, which is used by cicada algorithm manager to format the output data set.

The formater can take signal type object and generic Object signal to export.

Since:
V1.0
Version:
M1
Author:
nxi
